    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有第二人，取彼微塵，彼若干微塵數，爾所佛國土阿僧祇億百千萬那由他世界，過爾所世界為一步。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158a29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼人復過若干微塵數世界為一步，彼人如是過百千萬億那由他阿僧祇劫行乃下一塵，如是盡諸微塵。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是若干世界，若著微塵及不著者，滿中微塵，復更著十方世界。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過是世界，若著微塵及不著者，彼諸世界，下至水際，上至有頂，滿中微塵。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有第三人，取彼爾所微塵，過彼爾所微塵數世界為一步，彼若干百千萬億那由他阿僧祇劫行乃下一塵，如是盡諸微塵。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有第四人，取彼若干微塵數世界，若著微塵及不著者，下至水際，上至有頂，滿中微塵。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b11_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何，彼微塵可知數不？",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼若干微塵，可知其數，然彼同名釋迦牟尼佛，母同名摩訶摩耶，父同名輸頭檀，城同名迦毘羅，第一弟子同名舍利弗、目犍連，侍者弟子同名阿難陀，彼佛不可知數。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是第五人，第六、第七、第八、第九、第十人。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有第十一人，是人彼若干微塵中，取一微塵破為十方，若干世界微塵數分，如是餘微塵，亦悉破為若干世界微塵數分。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何，彼微塵分可知數不？",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復有人，彼若干微塵分佛國土為過一步，如是速疾神通行東方世界無量無邊劫下一微塵，東方盡如是微塵，若著微塵及不著者，下至水際，上至有頂，滿中微塵；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是南方乃至十方，下至水際，上至有頂，滿中微塵。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何，彼微塵可知數不？",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼若干微塵分，可知其數。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然現今在世同名釋迦牟尼佛，母同名摩訶摩耶，父同名輸頭檀王，城同名迦毘羅，第一弟子同名舍利弗、目犍連，侍者弟子同名阿難陀，不可數知。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何況種種異名佛、異名母、異名父、異名城、異名弟子、異名侍者。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我若干微塵數劫住世，說一同名釋迦牟尼，不可窮盡。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是同名然燈佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無同名提婆延佛　南無同名燈光明佛　南無同名一切勝佛　南無同名大稱佛　南無同名波頭摩勝佛　南無同名毘婆尸佛　南無同名尸棄佛　南無同名毘舍浮佛　南無同名拘留孫佛　南無同名拘那含佛　南無同名迦葉佛』「如是等異名母，乃至異名侍者，現在住世，我今悉知。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等應當一心敬禮。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若善男子、善女人，求阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，當先懺悔一切諸罪。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘犯四重罪，比丘尼犯八重罪，式叉摩那、沙彌、沙彌尼犯出家根本罪，若優婆塞犯優婆塞重戒，優婆夷犯優婆夷重戒，欲懺悔者，當淨洗浴、著新淨衣、不食葷辛；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當在靜處修治室內，以諸幡華莊嚴道場，香泥塗畫，懸四十九枚幡，莊嚴佛座，安置佛像；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒種種香，栴檀、沈水、薰陸、多伽羅、蘇犍陀，種種末香、塗香，燒如是等種種妙香，散種種華；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "興大慈悲願救苦眾生，未度者令度，未解者令解，未安者令安，未涅槃者令得涅槃；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0158c27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "晝夜思惟如來本行、苦行，於無量劫受諸苦惱，不生疲厭，為求無上菩提故，於一切眾生自生下心，如僮僕心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘懺四重罪，如是晝夜四十九日，當對八清淨比丘發露所犯罪，七日一對發露，至心慇重，悔昔所作，一心歸命十方諸佛，稱名禮拜，隨力隨分，如是至心，滿四十九日，罪必除滅。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人得清淨時當有相現，若於覺中、若於夢中，見十方諸佛與其記別，或見菩薩與其記別，將詣道場共為已伴；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或與摩頂示滅罪相；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或自見身入大會中，處在眾次；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或自見身處眾說法；",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或見諸師淨行沙門，將詣道場示其諸佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘懺悔罪時，若見如是相者，當知是人罪垢得滅，除不至心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘尼懺悔八重罪者，當如比丘法，滿足四十九日，當得清淨，除不至心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若式叉摩那、沙彌、沙彌尼懺悔根本重罪，當對四清淨比丘、比丘尼，如上法滿二十一日，當知清淨，除不至心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若優婆塞、優婆夷懺悔重戒罪，應當至心恭敬三寶，若見沙門，恭敬禮拜，生難遭想，當請詣道場，設種種供養，當請一比丘，心敬重者，就其發露所犯諸罪，至心懺悔，一心歸命十方諸佛，稱名禮拜，如是滿足七日，必得清淨，除不至心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊而說偈言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「得成菩提降伏魔，　　自在經行道樹下，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證無障礙眼及身，　　法界平等如虛空。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十億國土微塵數，　　菩薩弟子眾圍繞，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得於一切寂靜心，　　善住普賢諸行中。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛身相好妙莊嚴，　　放於種種無量光，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普照十方諸國土，　　諸佛不可思議力。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見佛國土悉無垢，　　無量妙色清淨滿，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛所有勝妙事，　　承佛神力見大眾。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方世界名寶幢，　　遠離諸垢妙莊嚴，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼處自在寶燈佛，　　於今現在彼世界。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「南方頗梨燈國土，　　清淨妙色普嚴淨，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摩尼清淨雲如來，　　現今在世說妙法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「西方無垢清淨土，　　名為安樂妙世界，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼自在佛無量壽，　　菩薩弟子現圍遶。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「北方世界名香燈，　　國土清淨甚嚴飾，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無染光幢佛所化，　　現今自在道場樹。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「琉璃光明真妙色，　　國土清淨勝莊嚴，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無礙光雲佛如來，　　於今現在東北方。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「光明照幢世界中，　　現見滿足諸菩薩，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自在吼聲佛彼處，　　現今在於東南方。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「種種樂樂佛世界，　　摩尼莊嚴妙無垢，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝妙智月如須彌，　　現見在於西南方。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「現見西北方如來，　　彌留光明平等界，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼處大聖自在佛，　　弟子菩薩眾圍遶。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「下方世界自在光，　　國土清淨寶炎藏，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光明妙輪不空見，　　佛今住彼妙國土。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「上方世界光炎藏，　　彼世界名淨無垢，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普眼功德光明雲，　　現見菩提樹下坐。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無上方普眼功德光明雲佛』」爾時，舍利弗等大眾，承佛神力，見十方過去、未來、現在諸佛，無量無邊。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，舍利弗在大眾中，悲泣流淚，白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「希有，世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，不發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者，不得成佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等昔來，猶如腐草，雖經春陽，無悕秋實。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，慧命舍利弗即從坐起，偏袒右肩，右膝著地，合掌白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願更廣說十方所有諸佛名號，我等樂聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝當至心諦聽，我為汝說。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得聞彼佛，一心敬禮。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此世界東方，過百千億世界，有佛世界名然燈，彼國土有佛名寶集阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無寶集佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，至心受持憶念，是善男子、善女人，畢竟得七覺分三昧，得不退轉阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心，超越世間六十劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊以偈頌曰：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「東方然燈界，　　有佛名寶集，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞名者，　　超世六十劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方有世界名寶集，彼世界有佛，名寶勝阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無寶勝佛』「若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，至心受持，憶念讀誦，合掌禮拜。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有善男子、善女人，以滿足三千大千世界珍寶布施，如是日日布施，滿足一百歲，如此布施福德，比前至心禮拜功德，百分不及一，千分不及一，百千分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不及一。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0159c29_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊以偈頌曰：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「寶集世界，　　有佛寶勝，　　若人聞名，",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "施不及一。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此東方，過八百世界，有佛世界名香積，彼世界有佛，名成就盧舍那阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，憶念禮拜，超越世間五百劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無成就盧舍那佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此世界，東方過千世界，名樹提跋提，彼世界有佛，名盧舍那鏡像阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子，善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，至心憶念，恭敬禮拜，得脫三惡道。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無盧舍那鏡像佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此東方，過二千世界，有佛國土名無量光明功德，彼界有佛名盧舍那光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，五體投地，深心敬重，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜，是人超越世間三十劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無盧舍那光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方過千世界，有佛國土名可樂，彼佛名不動應供、正遍知。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜，是人畢竟不退阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，一切諸魔所不能動。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無不動佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方過千世界，有佛國土名不可量，彼處有佛名大光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼光明佛名，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜，是人常不離一切諸佛菩薩，畢竟得不退轉阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無大光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從此世界，東方過六十千世界，有國土名然燈，佛名不可量聲阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼不可量聲佛名三稱者，是人畢竟不墮三惡道，定得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無無量聲如來』三稱「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過彼世界，度千佛國土，有世界名無塵，彼有佛名阿彌陀劬沙阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，深心敬重，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜，是人超越世間十二劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無阿彌陀劬沙佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過二十千佛國土，有世界名難勝，彼處有佛名大稱阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，合掌作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無大稱如來』「若復有人，以須彌山等七寶，日日布施，滿一百歲，比聞此佛名禮拜功德，百分不及一，乃至算數亦不及一。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過三千世界，有國土名光明，佛號寶光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，受持彼佛名，超越世間一百劫，得不退轉阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人不信聞名得如此功德者，是人定墮阿鼻地獄，滿足一百劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160b28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無寶光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方過十千國土，有世界名光明照，彼處有佛名得大無畏阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜，是人畢竟得大無畏，攝取無量無邊功德聚。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無得大無畏佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過第七千佛國土，有世界名摩尼光明，彼處有佛，名然燈火阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，至心恭敬禮拜，受持讀誦，是人攝得如來十力。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無然燈火佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過八千佛國土，有世界名真實，彼世界中有佛，號實聲阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，至心禮拜，是人畢竟得四聖諦，畢竟得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無實聲佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過二十千佛國土，有世界名光明，佛名無邊無垢阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現今說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，至心生信，受持讀誦，恭敬禮拜。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人，以滿三千大千世界七寶布施，比聞無垢佛名受持讀誦功德，千萬分不及一，乃至算數所不能及。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若眾生罪根深厚，不得聞無垢佛名。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，聞此如來名者，是人非於一佛所種諸善根，亦非十佛所種諸善根，是人乃是百千萬佛所種諸善根，是人超越世間四十八劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0160c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無無邊無垢佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方過九千佛國土，有世界名妙聲，佛號月聲阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，至心禮拜，是人所得一切功德白法，具足如滿月，畢竟得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無月聲佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過十千佛國土，有世界名無畏，佛名無邊稱阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，合掌作如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無無邊稱如來』「若復有人，以七寶如須彌山布施，日日如是，滿足百年，此福德聚比持佛名功德，百分不及一，乃至算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過千五百佛國土，有世界名然燈，佛號日月光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，聞彼佛名，受持讀誦，胡跪合掌，右膝著地，三稱如是言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無日月光明世尊』三稱「是人速成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過三十千佛國土，有世界名無垢，佛號無垢光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，天、龍、夜叉、羅剎，若人非人，聞是佛名，畢竟不退阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，不入惡道。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無無垢光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東方過十千佛國土，有世界名百光明，佛號清淨光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若天、龍、夜叉、人非人，聞名者，必得人身，遠離貪、瞋、癡煩惱。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞不信者，六十千劫墮大地獄。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無清淨光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過百佛國土，有世界名善德，佛號日光明阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人畢竟清淨心稱此佛名，所得功德，滿足如日輪，畢竟能降伏一切諸魔外道，超越世間三十劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無日光明佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過六十千佛國土，有世界名住七覺分，佛號無邊寶阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞彼佛名，是人具足得七覺分，能置眾生著勝寶中，畢竟成就無量功德聚。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無無邊寶佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過五百佛國土，有世界名華鏡像，佛號華勝阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞彼佛名，信心敬重，彼人一切善法成就，如華敷明，越度世間五十五劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無華勝佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過百千億佛國土，有世界名遠離一切憂惱，佛號妙身阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人聞彼佛名，至心敬禮，讀誦受持，是人決定遠離一切諸障，不入惡道，超越世間無量劫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無妙身佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復過那由他佛國土，有世界名平等，彼處有佛，號法光明清淨開敷蓮華阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀，現在說法。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人得聞彼如來名，受持不忘者，永離三惡道。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161b29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無法光明清淨開敷蓮華佛』「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若比丘、比丘尼、優婆塞、優婆夷，欲懺悔諸罪，當淨洗浴，著新淨衣，淨治室內，敷設高座，安置佛像，懸二十五枚幡，種種華香，供養誦念此二十五佛名，日夜六時懺悔，滿二十五日，滅四重八禁等罪，式叉摩那、沙彌沙彌尼亦如是。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，舍利弗復白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願如來演說過去七佛姓名、壽命長短，我等渴仰樂聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諦聽！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諦聽！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今為汝說。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c10_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去九十一劫，有佛名毘婆尸如來。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「過去三十劫，有佛名尸棄如來。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼劫中復有毘舍浮如來。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自此以後無量無數劫，空過無有佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至賢劫中有四佛：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「拘留孫佛，拘那含牟尼佛，迦葉佛，我釋迦牟尼佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛壽命八十千劫，尸棄佛壽命六十千劫，毘舍浮佛壽命二千劫，拘留孫佛壽命十四小劫，拘那含牟尼佛壽命三十小劫，迦葉佛壽命二十小劫，我現在最少壽命一百年。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛、尸棄佛、毘舍浮佛，剎利家生。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛、拘那含佛、迦葉佛，婆羅門家生。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，剎利家生。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛、尸棄佛、毘舍浮佛，此三佛姓拘隣。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛、拘那含牟尼佛、迦葉佛，此三佛姓迦葉。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，姓瞿曇。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，波叱羅樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，分陀利樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0161c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，娑羅樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，優頭跋樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含牟尼佛，尸利沙樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，尼拘律樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，阿說他樹下得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，三集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，三集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，再集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，一集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含牟尼佛，一集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，一集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，一集聲聞。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名吉沙，二名看茶。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名勝，二名自在。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名星宿，二名上。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名疾，二名力。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含牟尼佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名活丹治，二名毘頭羅。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名輸那，二名頗羅墮。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，第一聲聞弟子，一名舍利弗，二名目揵連。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上二人等，前者智慧第一，後神通第一。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，侍者名無憂。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，侍者名離畏。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a21_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，侍者名寂。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，侍者名智。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含文尼佛，侍者名親。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，侍者名迦夫。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，侍者名歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，子名成陰。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，子名不可量。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，子名善智。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，子名上。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含文尼佛，子名勝。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，子名導師。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我釋迦牟尼佛，子名羅睺羅。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「毘婆尸佛，父名槃頭，母名槃頭意，城名槃頭。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162a29_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尸棄佛，父名鉤那，母名勝，城名阿樓那跋提。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘舍浮佛，父名阿樓那天子，母名稱意，城名隨意。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘留孫佛，父婆羅門種，名功德，母名廣，彼天子名無畏，城亦名無畏。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "拘那含文尼佛，父婆羅門種，名火丹大德，母名難勝，天子名莊嚴，城亦名莊嚴。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉佛，父婆羅門種，名淨德，母名善才，天子名知使，城亦名知使，今時波羅奈城是。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今父名輸頭檀王，母名摩訶摩耶，城名迦毘羅。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利弗！",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應當敬禮我本師，謂釋迦牟尼佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『南無稱妙佛　南無降伏一切佛　南無然燈光佛　南無無畏佛　南無法勝佛』「如是等，初一大阿僧祇劫，有八十億佛，最後名釋迦牟尼佛。",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二阿僧祇劫初：",
        "from": "T14n0440_008:0162b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
